back\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 19, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lpo1665702578918.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lpo1665702578918.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lpo1665702578918.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lpo1665702578918\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__done_216266\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Exit from the ProcScript module without changing <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__topic_d71210e1_d71211e1_d71212e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__p_d71213e1_d71214e1_d71215e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__topic_d46812e1_d46813e1_d46814e1_d46815e1_d46816e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594444e68\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__p_d71219e1_d71220e1_d71221e1\">None. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span> statement does not affect <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__topic_d46817e1_d46818e1_d46819e1_d46820e1_d46821e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594444e83\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__topic_d46822e1_d46823e1_d46824e1_d46825e1_d46826e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594444e92\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lpo1665702578918__p_d71231e1_d71232e1_d71233e1\">The statement <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span> immediately exits from the ProcScript module. If you want to return a value, use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">return</span> statement rather than <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger quit\nif ($formmod = 0)\n done\nelse\n message \"Data modified!! Use STORE before QUIT.\"\n return (-1)\nendif\nend; quit\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrg1665702578278.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>break</a><p>Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by for, forentity, forlist, repeat, or while.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjw1665702578992.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>end</a><p>Marks the end of a ProcScript module, operation, or trigger.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hyy1665702577902.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>exit</a><p>Exits the current component instance and returns to the previous or specified instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckg1665702579864.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>return</a><p>Exit from the ProcScript module, optionally returning a value to $status.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529667\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529667\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "done Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 19, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Exit from the ProcScript module without changing $status . done Return Values None. The done statement does not affect $status . Use Allowed in all component types. Description The statement done immediately exits from the ProcScript module. If you want to return a value, use the return statement rather than done . The following example shows how to use the done statement: trigger quit if ($formmod = 0) done else message \"Data modified!! Use STORE before QUIT.\" return (-1) endif end; quit Copy Related Links break Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by for, forentity, forlist, repeat, or while. end Marks the end of a ProcScript module, operation, or trigger. exit Exits the current component instance and returns to the previous or specified instance. return Exit from the ProcScript module, optionally returning a value to $status. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}